  "prompt": "Which IIT has best Hostel Rooms?",
  "response": "The quality of hostel rooms in Indian Institutes of Technology (IITs) can vary significantly depending on factors like infrastructure, maintenance, and amenities provided. Some IITs are widely recognized for having better hostel facilities, including:\n\n1. **IIT Bombay**: Known for its sprawling campus and well-maintained hostels, IIT Bombay offers a variety of accommodation options.\n\n2. **IIT Delhi**: IIT Delhi has good hostel facilities with ample amenities, and the hostels are generally well-equipped.\n\n3. **IIT Madras**: The hostels at IIT Madras are known for their spaciousness and good living conditions.\n\n4. **IIT Kharagpur**: It has a large campus and some of the oldest hostels, which have been renovated and maintained well.\n\n5. **IIT Roorkee**: The hostels are comfortable and have decent facilities, making it a popular choice among students.\n\nUltimately, \"best\" is subjective and can depend on individual preferences like room size, shared or single occupancy, cleanliness, and other amenities. Visiting the campuses and checking reviews from current students can provide better insights into the hostel experiences at each IIT.",
